# Liabilities Insurance Case Estimates Net Reinsurance And Non Reinsurance Recoveries Amount

## identifier
de8557

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of net case estimates included in the outstanding claims provision as at the relevant date. 

For the purposes of this item, case estimates must be reported:
     - as the balance outstanding at the relevant date;
     - net of reinsurance recoveries;
     - net of non-reinsurance recoveries; and
     - excluding IBNR/IBNER, claims handling expenses and risk margins.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Liabilities.Insurance.CaseEstimatesNetReinsuranceAndNonReinsuranceRecoveries.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo3.02.05
- period=instant
